      <h2 id="profit-margins-breakdown">Profit Margins Breakdown</h2>

      <div class="prose">
        <p>Revenue tells only half the story. Profit margins reveal which business model actually puts more money in your pocket. Here's the detailed breakdown based on actual 2026 contractor data:</p>
      </div>

